{"tid":151821,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d廢老好串, 讓關愛座俾佢都唔坐","createTime":"2017-03-11T08:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T13:03:16.000Z","uid":73783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8666880f5cc01dc1d92f83b1485c3f0e1b45d027","tid":151821,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我見架車滿晒, 無位<br />\n剩返2個關愛座無人坐<br />\nd人寧願企都無坐<br />\n我企左成日, 咁攰<br />\n無理由唔坐架麻<br />\n最多見到廢老先讓返位俾佢地<br />\n<br />\n說時遲, 那時快<br />\n坐唔夠3分鐘<br />\n到下個站<br />\n有個廢老坐住架輪椅入左黎<br />\n見佢企都企唔到咁可憐<br />\n就讓個關愛座俾佢坐la<br />\n點知佢視而不見<br />\n可能個廢老睇唔到姐<br />\n所以我送佛送到西<br />\n同佢講: 伯伯, 個位俾你坐嫁<br />\n點知佢一句: 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我究竟做錯左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a4d76ef4375ce0aea1c0bfb33a2cea16bbafe","tid":151821,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"衰在太好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n善良只限用黎對自己好朋友同埋屋企人, 對街外人要狠心D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7362cc6252925452d5ac47b71faf7bbffdc840de","tid":151821,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a4762b774335e78dd27564c7a923073739f35a","tid":151821,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77efdb4afca9b6c2831c101021209e642acbcb4a","tid":151821,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0992a68468a69f2af4c85500138215d010253c","tid":151821